{"tid":1794492,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"既然跨年有咁高既媒體曝光率,我覺得可以咁做","createTime":"2019-12-23T06:55:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T07:29:26.000Z","uid":310474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e924a4fd8cdc024470dc1bb56ba30eb958a8c69b","tid":1794492,"uid":310474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T06:55:33.000Z","msg":"(處女post) <br />\n每次跨年都可以話係全球一齊狂歡既日子,但係依個時候香港就有催淚彈煙花與民歡度一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,可想<ins>全球既媒體都會報道,係咁時候不如好好利用做宣傳</ins>。<br />\n<br />\n以往都見到一d post 話一d支持香港既外國人知道要stand with HK, 但唔知可以做咩實際上幫到手,所以我覺得可以由依家開始直到跨年係twitter等既地方宣傳<span style=\"color: red;\">2020一月停買中國貨品行動</span>,<ins>充份咁使用/團結我們係各地既人力,亦都令更多外國人關注香港</ins>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n目前只係一個構想,係呼籲停買中國貨定係其他行動可以再諗下<br />\n<br />\n#2020Jan-NoChineseGoods"},{"pid":"ab25de903ed7070a066de8dfc622f49dd7404024","tid":1794492,"uid":310474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T06:56:25.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到"},{"pid":"8a250337216208acf72a59a3d61519ddafaafa94","tid":1794492,"uid":114487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T06:57:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VgwZ4tD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVgwZ4tD.jpg&h=52b479a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TGepv8D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTGepv8D.jpg&h=265d7544&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ocgLfAm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FocgLfAm.jpg&h=e2a8e121&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"19678dea109dcf8d4318130614ad95da35ad1b9f","tid":1794492,"uid":310474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T07:08:54.000Z","msg":"擁"},{"pid":"ce6774c4c1e26cf861a7cca1d0be0f9cbeb9c907","tid":1794492,"uid":310474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T07:09:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e03a4f7707ea9